'''雪米糍'''（{{lang-en|Mochi ice cream}}）又稱'''麻糬冰淇淋'''，是一種使用搗碎的[[糯稻|糯米]]並加入冰淇淋的[[冰品|冰品]]甜點，這是最初由日裔美国人{{link-en|弗朗西絲·橋本|Frances Hashimoto}}与其丈夫在美国[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[小东京|小东京]]發明的食品<ref name="latimes">{{cite news|first=Teresa|last=Watanabe|title=Frances Hashimoto dies at 69; Little Tokyo leader, mochi ice cream creator |url= http://articles.latimes.com/2012/nov/07/local/la-me-frances-hashimoto-20121107 |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2012-11-07 |accessdate=2012-12-02}}</ref>。

== 描述 ==
雪米糍是一種將[[圆|圓狀]]糯米加入冰淇淋的冰品甜點，其冰淇淋味道增加了甜味以及質感<ref name="Mikawaya_what">{{cite web|url=http://www.mochiicecream.com/what-is-mochi-ice-cream/|title=What is Mochi Ice Cream?|publisher=Mikawaya|language=en|accessdate=2016-03-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405215542/http://www.mochiicecream.com/what-is-mochi-ice-cream/|archivedate=2016年4月5日|df=}}</ref>。使用成分包含如[[香草|香草]]、[[巧克力|巧克力]]和[[草莓|草莓]]調味的冰淇淋和其他如[[科納咖啡|科納咖啡]]、[[果酒|水果酒]]、[[紅豆|紅豆]]等<ref name="Mikawaya_flav">{{cite web |url=http://www.mochiicecream.com/mochi-ice-cream/ |title=Mochi Ice Cream |publisher=Mikawaya |language=en |accessdate=2016-03-25 |archive-date=2016-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405205541/http://www.mochiicecream.com/mochi-ice-cream/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>；也可補充冰淇淋並用[[马铃薯|马铃薯]]或者[[玉米澱粉|玉米澱粉]]處理以防止[[形狀|形狀]]改變<ref name="Mikawaya_what"/><ref name="HoJ recipe">{{cite web|title=Mochi Ice Cream Recipe|url=http://www.houseofjapan.com/cuisine/mochi-ice-cream-recipe|publisher=House of Japan|date=2010-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610050951/http://www.houseofjapan.com/cuisine/mochi-ice-cream-recipe|archivedate=2015-06-10}}</ref>。

